--Login Test Scenarios --
<Valid login test scenarios>------
verify login using a valid e-mail and valid password
verify login using a valid mobile number with different forms [with country code has formats like [+20, 002,...etc} and without country code ] and valid password
verify login using a valid English and Arabic formats mobile number with different forms [with country code has formats like [+20, 002,...etc} and without country code ] and a valid password
verify forgot password redirect correctly
verify that creating an account redirect correctly
verify create page redirect correctly

<Invalid login test scenarios>------
verify login using valid e-mail and invalid password
verify login using an invalid e-mail and valid password
verify login using an invalid e-mail format and a valid password
verify login using an invalid e-mail and invalid password
verify login using a valid mobile number and an invalid password
verify login using an invalid mobile number and a valid password
verify login using an invalid mobile number and invalid password
verify empty e-mail and empty password
verify login using valid e-mail and old changed password
verify login using old changed e-mail and valid password
